      "rationale": "Gait simulator (MTS 858 Mini Bionix) programmed with ISO 14243-1 force-displacement profiles; load cell calibration traceable to NIST standards. Synovial fluid simulant (0.5% carboxymethylcellulose in PBS) viscosity measured at 8.2 mPa·s (target 8.0 mPa·s, within ±3%). Bath temperature maintained at 37.0 ± 0.4 °C via recirculating heater."
