      },
      "rationale": "CFD-predicted peak particle concentration of 4.3 × 10^6 particles/mL compared against fluorescence measurement of 4.0 × 10^6 particles/mL (relative error 7.5%, within 15% criterion). Spatial overlap of top-quartile concentration zones between CFD and experiment: 87%, exceeding the 80% threshold."
