      "rationale": "Independent review of simulation setup performed by senior CFD engineer (not the primary analyst) using checklist CR-TKR-001 covering 38 items. Zero critical discrepancies identified; two minor documentation gaps corrected prior to final run. Review sign-off recorded in project quality record QR-TKR-2024-003."
