        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Model inputs acceptance criteria",
        "description": "All material properties (fluid viscosity, particle density, geometry dimensions) must have documented sources with uncertainty bounds; boundary conditions must be traceable to experimental measurements or published physiological data; input uncertainty propagated through UQ study."
      },
      "rationale": "Synovial fluid density (1008 ± 5 kg/m³) and viscosity parameters sourced from three independent literature references and confirmed by in-house viscometry. UHMWPE particle density (935 ± 10 kg/m³) from manufacturer datasheet. Tibial tray geometry from CT scan (voxel size 0.1 mm). Gait loading boundary conditions from ISO 14243-1. Full uncertainty propagation performed via Monte Carlo sampling (n = 500) documented in UQ report UQR-TKR-2024."
