        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Test samples acceptance criteria",
        "description": "At least three tibial tray specimens from the same manufacturing lot used for validation testing; dimensional inspection confirms specimens are within nominal tolerance (±0.1 mm on critical dimensions)."
      },
      "rationale": "Five tibial tray specimens from manufacturing lot TKR-2023-L07 used for in-vitro validation. Dimensional inspection (CMM, traceable to NIST) confirmed all specimens within ±0.05 mm of nominal on critical clearance dimensions. Lot traceability documentation archived in test record TR-TKR-2024-001."
